{"tid":1937063,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民接受訪問，解釋西九投贊成票一事","createTime":"2020-03-21T16:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T16:32:56.000Z","uid":60916,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7efb45b340b488f6cb2d20a9406160027ce2eedd","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"民主黨支持西九文化區工程，通過的約188億元撥款，包括西九地庫餘下的綜合地庫2區工程約174億元。其餘款項之用途，包括興建一條行人天橋接駁九龍站圓方和西九的M+博物館，加強步行的暢達性。民主派其他議員對西九項目曾有些爭議，我們是理解的；但投票前議員或公眾並無表示過要求我們在財委會推翻有關工程，不少藝術表演者一直都希望西九文化區可以早日落成，改善社區環境及藝術文化推廣。市民也不希望西九文化區再拖下去或中途夭折。<br />\n<br />\n想睇全文禁入去睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470054-20190723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470054-20190723.htm&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=7fda4a7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470054-20190723.htm&h=97366042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470054-20190723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4de616d85d7c525c9e4d104e4b90c168c273d2fe","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:02:13.000Z","msg":"幫泛民洗底"},{"pid":"91f15a9b7534bdb4ee984d90c8223e4d38b9b251","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d3e444d1a87cd8ca88f0e1b9a304a1e0b44261","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e2e157fb845354a06e634026f10906b28821bba","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"轟啊"},{"pid":"db42e3a19314d61426e4c0560e99f09035c5e401","tid":1937063,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:05:13.