熱血公民票<br />\n今日就鳩沙田友既票<br />\n咁就送左席比民賤聯<br />\n道歉Sorry好撚假囉<br />\n人地議席就無左咩都無<br />\n你地今次就大勝食咁多議席<br />\n仲要好多區比你地逼到退選讓路含淚投<br />\n<br />\n既然你地食人血饅頭食得咁開心<br />\n手足陣間不如發夢去是旦一個白鴿黨既辦事署裝下修<br />\n反正你地今次賺咁多經費咁多人工<br />\n比2條路你地揀<br />\n裝修/捐一半人工做抗爭基金<br />\n就係咁</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>新口號同洗腦金句！想贏既入嚟同我宣傳出去 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>將香港人 反抗<br />\n變做<br />\n香港人 返工<br />\n成個口號幾撚震撼</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>保護休班警,你我有責 - #4</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔好搞休班警<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動識女溝女有咩問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>CCtai班友仔做咩咁敏感<br />\n大家都係有相同興趣同諗法<br />\n傾得埋再交換contact上埋床有咩問題<br />\nCCTai班小朋友真係大驚小怪</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;pos